Somehow, we turned a corner tonight and worked together. We even did a holiday swap on the fly that worked for us both! It was super refreshing.
I hope we keep it up. This week will be super crazy for me. I'll get as much done as I can but will really need help getting us out of the beach next
week.
We also agree that we need to have a conversation before the kids start seeing all this stuff disappearing to "Dad's place".  Let's think about that asap.
I'm telling you because you will be in work mode soon, so I just want this on your radar. I'll do my damn best this week, but please budget time for
this soon.
thanks!
